Rapper Boitumelo Thulo, popularly known as Boity, will be embarking on the tour of her reality show titled Own Your Throne. Own Your Throne is set to premiere on Wednesday, 5-February this year on BET Africa DStv channel 129 at 21:30. The tour will begin next Sunday at Altitude Beach in Fourways, Johannesburg. The television presenter tweeted that she will announce more venues soon. "Hey, Fam!! So I’ll be kicking off my #OwnYourThroneBET tour soon and the only info I have right now is EVERYONE IS INVITED! I’d love to celebrate with y’all! I’ll be posting more venues soon," the tweet read. The line-up for the launch party includes Major League DJs, Kamo Mphela, DBN Gogo and Pink Molly. 